- Step-1 : Open Project
- Step-2 : Open the project path
- Step-3 : Open app--->src--->main--->java
- Step-4 : Right click on package--->new--->click on kotlin class/file--->name of the file.


--->Kotlin says that concatenation is hevay
- So to avoid we use "$" symbol
- We can also perform mathematical operations directly in the print statements by using "$ and {}"
- The value in the var can be changed but while in the val we cannot change the values